'''布萊德利·富勒'''（{{lang-en|Bradley Fuller}}）是一名美國製片人，他與[[麥可·貝|麥可·貝]]、[[安德魯·福姆|安德魯·福姆]]合夥持有[[白金沙丘|白金沙丘]]<ref name=future>{{cite web| url= https://filmschoolrejects.com/the-purge-producer-brad-fuller-on-the-future-of-platinum-dunes| title= ‘The Purge’ Producer Brad Fuller on The Future of Platinum Dunes| first= Jack| last= Giroux| date= 2013-06-07| website= filmschoolrejects.com| access-date= 2016-05-22| archive-date= 2020-11-08| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20201108090440/https://filmschoolrejects.com/the-purge-producer-brad-fuller-on-the-future-of-platinum-dunes-28f427d179a3/| dead-url= no}}</ref>。

== 早期生活 ==
布萊德·富勒於1987年畢業於[[康乃狄克州|康乃狄克州]]的[[衛斯理大學|衛斯理大學]]<ref name=WeslyanFilmStudies>{{cite web| url= http://www.wesleyan.edu/filmstudies/SpecialEvents/past-special-events.html| publisher= Film Studies Department, Weskeyan University| title= Pictures from Past Events| access-date= 2016-05-22| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160516204919/http://wesleyan.edu/filmstudies/SpecialEvents/past-special-events.html| archive-date= 2016-05-16}}</ref><ref name=TexasCast>{{cite web | url= http://www.visualhollywood.com/movies/texaschainsaw_begin/cast.php | title= The Texas Chainsaw Massacre: Cast and Crew | website= visualhollywood.com | access-date= 2011-02-04 | archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20110723051108/http://www.visualhollywood.com/movies/texaschainsaw_begin/cast.php | archive-date= 2011-07-23}}</ref>。他未來的合夥人[[麥可·貝|麥可·貝]]也是該學校的校友（1986年）<ref name=WeslyanFilmStudies />。導演[[喬斯·溫登|喬斯·溫登]]和[[米格·奧提塔|米格·奧提塔]]也是富勒在衛斯理大學的同班同學<ref name=future />。

== 個人生活 ==
富勒和他的妻子亞歷珊卓（Alexandra）有兩個兒子：演員卡麥隆（Cameron）<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.imdb.com/name/nm0298189/|title=Cameron Fuller|website=Internet Movie Database|access-date=2015-10-14|archive-date=2015-11-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151113164255/http://www.imdb.com/name/nm0298189/|dead-url=no}}</ref>和弟弟帕克斯頓（Paxton）。

